What is Workshiftly

Workshiftly is a Time Tracking and Productivity Monitoring Solution. We envisioned creating a product to improve the overall productivity and accurate management of resources by implementing best time management practices. This is a true Saas Application designed with a non-demanding onboarding process and a user-friendly interface.

With Workshiftly, you can monitor the activities of your employees during the work hours, their daily timeline, overall productivity, attendance and breaks, and track the status of allocated projects and tasks.

By tracking the daily activities of your employees you can increase efficiency, manage and allocate resources, maintain accurate records such as attendance reports, estimate time allocation for tasks and projects and utilize historical data for future predictions and management.
